OL,3,CChannel Islands included in UK Rwanda
OL,4,Cbill without governments' consent
OL,6,FThere are frustrations that the
OL,7,FBritish Government has automatically
OL,8,Fincluded and in a draft law aimed at
OL,9,Fdeterring boat crossings across the
OL,10,FEnglish Channel .
OL,12,FThe two self-governing jurisdictions
OL,13,Fare not part of the United Kingdom and
OL,14,Fare Crown Dependencies, meaning their
OL,15,Frelationship stems from the Monarchy
OL,16,Frather than the UK Parliament.
