OL,6,FGuernsey's Home Affairs President says
OL,7,Fit is "very important" that
OL,8,Fpoliticians in Westminster understand
OL,9,Fthe islands' constitutional rights to
OL,10,Fset its own legislation.
OL,12,FDeputy Rob Prow said: "Where we need
OL,13,Fto be in our relationship with the UK
OL,14,Fis not having these misunderstandings
OL,15,Fand I think it's very important that
OL,16,Fthe UK understand this. The
OL,17,Frelationship with Guernsey and Jersey
OL,18,Fdoes recognise our independence."
