OL,3,CChannel Islands included in UK Rwanda
OL,4,Cbill without governments' consent
OL,6,FJersey's External Relations Minister,
OL,7,FDeputy Ian Gorst, added: "I've said to
OL,8,FUK Ministers that it's disappointing
OL,9,Fwe weren't consulted.
OL,11,F"We currently have no intention of
OL,12,Fhaving the Rwanda bill extended to
OL,13,FJersey, nor do I think to any of the
OL,14,Fother Crown Dependencies."
OL,16,FDeputy Gorst explained that it appears
OL,17,Fto be an administrative oversight and
OL,18,FMinisters have reassured him that they
OL,19,Fwill consult Channel Islands'
OL,20,Fgovernments in future to respect their
OL,21,Fautonomy.
