OL,6,FThat appears not to have happened in
OL,7,Fthis case and that is what is causing
OL,8,Fthe concern.
OL,10,FThe reality is it is unlikely to have
OL,11,Fany practical effect on Jersey and
OL,12,FGuernsey.
OL,14,FThis is in many ways a matter of
OL,15,Fprinciple rather than practice.
OL,17,FEven if the legislation is passed in
OL,18,Fthe UK, it realistically won't be
OL,19,Factivated in Jersey and Guernsey
OL,20,Fwithout their consent.
